mmc2: cqhci: Doorbell:  0xbf01dfff | TCN:      0x00000000
mmc2: cqhci: Dev queue: 0x00000000 | Dev Pend: 0x08000000
mmc2: cqhci: Task clr:  0x00000000 | SSC1:     0x00011000
