mmc2: cqhci: RED mask:  0xfdf9a080 | TERRI:    0x00000000
mmc2: cqhci: Resp idx:  0x0000000d | Resp arg: 0x00000000
mmc2: sdhci: ============ SDHCI REGISTER DUMP ===========
mmc2: sdhci: Sys addr:  0x7c722000 | Version:  0x00000002
